<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Booking Confirmation</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Booking Confirmation</h1>
    <p>Dear <%= @passenger.name %>,</p>
    <p>Thank you for booking a flight with our website. Your booking has been confirmed.</p>
    <p>Flight details:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Flight number: <%= @booking.flight_id %></li>
      <li>Departure: <%= @booking.flight.departure_airport %></li>
      <li>Destination: <%= @booking.flight.arrival_airport %></li>
      <li>Date: <%= @booking.flight.depart_date %></li>
      <li>Time: <%= @booking.flight.depart_time %></li>
    </ul>
    <p>Please keep this email for your records.</p>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>The Team</p>
  </body>
</html>